    • Vehicle

      public Vehicle(String ID, String manufacturer, String model, double purchasePrice, boolean morePassengers, Malfunction malfunction)
      Constructs a new Vehicle with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      ID - the unique identifier for the vehicle
      manufacturer - the manufacturer of the vehicle
      model - the model of the vehicle
      purchasePrice - the purchase price of the vehicle
      morePassengers - indicates if the vehicle can carry more passengers
      malfunction - the malfunction details of the vehicle, if any

    • chargeBattery

      public void chargeBattery(int amount)
      Charges the battery of the vehicle by the specified amount. If the resulting battery level exceeds 100%, it is capped at 100%. Also sets the emptyBattery flag to false.
      Parameters:
      amount - the amount to charge the battery

    • dischargeBattery

      public void dischargeBattery(int amount)
      Discharges the battery of the vehicle by the specified amount. If the resulting battery level falls below 10%, it is set to 10% and the emptyBattery flag is set to true.
      Parameters:
      amount - the amount to discharge the battery

    • repair

      public void repair()
      Repairs the vehicle by setting the malfunction attribute to null. This indicates that the vehicle no longer has a malfunction.
